Directory structure
===================
   test_pic_1d2v_vm_cart        -- executable (simulation)
   params_pic_1d2v_vm_cart      -- input file
   README                       -- info (this file)
   run/                         -- output directory

HOWTO
=====
0. Create output directory if missing, and move into it
     $ mkdir run
     $ cd run

1. Run parallel simulation within directory
     $ mpirun -np 2 ../../../bin/test_pic_1d2v_vm_cart params_pic_1d2v_vm_cart.nml
